title: September Debuts: Not Reading comics is... such a waste of time!
description:
"Not Reading Debuts" ( <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading+Debuts" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading+Debuts</a>  ) are part of the <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading</a>  project, and contain all first issues published and/or released during a given month that made an uploader's personal cut.

The month being September 2014 and the uploader being me in this case, obviously.

This instalment contains the following current debuts:


   Oddly Normal #1 - Image        - Adventure / Fantasy / Humour

   Sundowners   #1 - Dark Horse   - Mystery / Superhero / Supernatural

   The Names    #1 - Vertigo      - Crime / Drama / Mystery

   Wild's End   #1 - Boom Studios - Disaster / Historical / Sci-Fi


Four titles, four publishers; the only unusual aspect being the total lack of
anything unusual, this time 'round! :P

Additionally, there're two bonus files, just like last month: The original version of "Oddly Normal" from about ten years ago, of which the current issue is little more than a slightly nicer reprint; and my own compilation of the first volume of "Concrete Park", serialized in "Dark Horse Presents" three years ago, due to this month's debut of the second volume ( <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/10965287" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/10965287</a>  ).
